		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />FCEU-ABCSOUP refers to the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alphabet_soup" class="postlink">alphabet soup</a> of FCE Ultra debugger mods: FCEUD, FCEUXD, FCEUXD SP, FCEUX, etc. Readers can substitute their favorite.

		

